ur password is VMi followed by your 7 digit Colleague ID number  Example    Email address username mail vmi edu  Password   VMi0123456   Note the upper and lower case letters followed by   numbers beginning with zero and not the letter  o  Please make sure you are NOT using an old bookmark or favorite links  DELETE any old bookmark favorite links  Use either of these links  http vmiconnect vmi edu or http www outlook com mail vmi edu  If you use any email apps  including Outlook  on your computer  tablet  or mobile phone  you MUST update your password to match your new Office 365 password  If you are still unable to login to your VMI email  please take your photo ID to the Barracks Help Desk so your password can be reset if necessary  The Microsoft email platform on which VMIconnect resides is being upgraded to Office 365 on Monday  January 28  2013  specific time to be announced in upcoming email  Your email will be moved to Office 365  but your SkyDrive data will remain on your Live edu account  Cadet passwords for VMI email and MS SkyDrive will be RESET on Monday  January 28  2013  THIS WILL NOT AFFECT CADET VMI NETWORK PASSWORDS  The new password for both sites will be emailed to cadets Note the upper and lower case letters followed by numbers beginning with  zero  and not the letter  o  Cadet usernames will not change  HOW TO ACCESS YOUR CADET EMAIL  Go to http vmiconnect vmi edu or http www outlook com mail vmi edu  IT suggests that cadets bookmark these links  Enter your username  Enter your password   Cadets will be forced to change their password  If any email apps  including Outlook  are used on a cadet computer  tablet  or mobile phone  the password MUST updated to match the new Office 365 password  HOW TO ACCESS YOUR CADET SKYDRIVE  Go to http skydrive com  IT suggests that cadets bookmark this link  Enter your username  Enter your password  Cadets will not be forced to change your password for SkyDrive  however  it is strongly recommend that you do so to ensure the security of your account  NOTE  VMI no longer administers this SkyDrive account  As a result  passwords cannot be reset should users be unable to login  If cadets need this account password reset  they will need to go to  https account live com ResetPassword aspx   Please direct any questions or needs of assistance to the Barracks Help Desk or call 540 464 7888  Cadets can also visit the FAQ page for answers to frequently asked questions and additional information regarding the upgrade    VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health   Safety   IT   Site Index Parents   Families   Cadets   Non discrimination Statement   Privacy   THE VMI PHILOSOPHY The VMI experience is framed by relevant education within a military environment  It s an education that develops character  fosters a lifelong appreciation of physical fitness engenders a sense of responsibility to others  and cultivates the ability to master adversity  VIRGINIA MILITARY INSTITUTE Lexington  Virginia 24450 General Information   540  464 7230  Admissions  admissions vmi edu 